      <title>makdown的书写(一)</title>
      <link href="/2023/07/09/makdown%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A6%E5%86%99(%E4%B8%80)/"/>
      <url>/2023/07/09/makdown%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A6%E5%86%99(%E4%B8%80)/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text&#x2F;css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/hexo-tag-hint@0.3.1/dist/hexo-tag-hint.min.css"><p>项目结构分为静态和Hexo两部分，静态文章用于部署</p><h3 id="用的命令"><a href="#用的命令" class="headerlink" title="用的命令"></a>用的命令</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-angular2html" data-language="angular2html"><code class="language-angular2html">hexo g 生成静态网页hexo d 部署githexo s 启动本地服务器<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="bilibili视频引入标签"><a href="#bilibili视频引入标签" class="headerlink" title="bilibili视频引入标签"></a>bilibili视频引入标签</h3><p>your_video_id 是b站的bv号或av号。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-angular2html" data-language="angular2html"><code class="language-angular2html">&#123;% bilicard your_video_id %&#125; <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><div class="bvideo"><a href="//www.bilibili.com/video/BV1we4y1Y7qW" target="_blank">        <div class="bvideo-box">            <div class="bvideo-cover">                <div class="cover-default"></div>                <div class="bvideo-cover-layer" style="background-image:url(https://pic1.xuehuaimg.com/proxy/http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/650c48a3a7ec12a695a0fc580d5ccdb283a978dd.jpg)">                    <i class="icon-video"></i>                </div>                <span class="duration">00:03:52</span>            </div>            <div class="bvideo-info">                <p class="title">张学友《天黑黑》翻唱</p>                <p class="card-status">                    <span class="play-num">                        <i class="fa fa-youtube-play"></i>                        <span>1536</span></span>                    <span>                        <i class="fa fa-list-alt"></i>                        <span>0</span></span></p>                <div class="partition">                    <label class="card-label">视频</label>                    <label class="up-label"></label>                    <label class="up-name">火星海盗Mic</label>                </div>                <div class="actions hide"></div>            </div>        </div>    </a></div><h3 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">[我是内联样式的链接](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.google.com)[我是带有标题的内联样式链接](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.google.com &quot;Google&#39;s Homepage&quot;)[是参考样式的链接][Arbitrary case-insensitive reference text][我是存储库文件的相对引用](..&#x2F;blob&#x2F;master&#x2F;LICENSE)[可以将数字用于引用样式的链接定义][1]或者将其留空并使用 [这是链接][arbitrary case-insensitive reference text]: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hexo.io[1]: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hexo.io&#x2F;docs&#x2F;[这是链接]: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hexo.io&#x2F;api&#x2F;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><a href="https://www.google.com/">我是内联样式的链接</a></p><p><a href="https://www.google.com/" title="Google&#39;s Homepage">我是带有标题的内联样式链接</a></p><p><a href="https://hexo.io/">是参考样式的链接</a></p><p><a href="../blob/master/LICENSE">我是存储库文件的相对引用</a></p><p><a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">可以将数字用于引用样式的链接定义</a></p><p>或者将其留空并使用 <a href="https://hexo.io/api/">这是链接</a></p><h3 id="水平线"><a href="#水平线" class="headerlink" title="水平线"></a>水平线</h3><hr><p>虚线</p><hr><p>星号</p><hr><p>下划线</p><h3 id="分隔符"><a href="#分隔符" class="headerlink" title="分隔符"></a>分隔符</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Markdown</th><th>Less</th><th>Pretty</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><em>Still</em></td><td><code>renders</code></td><td><strong>nicely</strong></td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-angular2html" data-language="angular2html"><code class="language-angular2html">|                |ASCII                          |HTML                         ||----------------|-------------------------------|-----------------------------||Single backticks|&#96;&#39;Isn&#39;t this fun?&#39;&#96;            |&#39;Isn&#39;t this fun?&#39;            ||Quotes          |&#96;&quot;Isn&#39;t this fun?&quot;&#96;            |&quot;Isn&#39;t this fun?&quot;            ||Dashes          |&#96;-- is en-dash, --- is em-dash&#96;|-- is en-dash, --- is em-dash|<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><table><thead><tr><th></th><th>ASCII</th><th>HTML</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Single backticks</td><td><code>&#39;Isn&#39;t this fun?&#39;</code></td><td>‘Isn’t this fun?’</td></tr><tr><td>Quotes</td><td><code>&quot;Isn&#39;t this fun?&quot;</code></td><td>“Isn’t this fun?”</td></tr><tr><td>Dashes</td><td><code>-- is en-dash, --- is em-dash</code></td><td>– is en-dash, — is em-dash</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="标签显示"><a href="#标签显示" class="headerlink" title="标签显示"></a>标签显示</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-angular2html" data-language="angular2html"><code class="language-angular2html">&lt;p&gt;To reboot your computer, press &lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;&#x2F;kbd&gt;+&lt;kbd&gt;alt&lt;&#x2F;kbd&gt;+&lt;kbd&gt;del&lt;&#x2F;kbd&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>To reboot your computer, press <kbd>ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>alt</kbd>+<kbd>del</kbd>.</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">&lt;dl&gt;    &lt;dt&gt;定义列表&lt;&#x2F;dt&gt;    &lt;dd&gt;小一号的字，这是小一号的字&lt;&#x2F;dd&gt;    213    &lt;dt&gt;Markdown in HTML&lt;&#x2F;dt&gt;    &lt;dd&gt;Does *not* work **very** well. Use HTML &lt;em&gt;tags&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;dd&gt;&lt;&#x2F;dl&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><dl>    <dt>定义列表</dt>    <dd>小一号的字，这是小一号的字</dd>    213    <dt>Markdown in HTML</dt>    <dd>Does *not* work **very** well. Use HTML <em>tags</em>.</dd></dl><dl>  <dt>Definition list</dt>  <dd>Is something people use sometimes.</dd>  <dt>Markdown in HTML</dt>  <dd>Does *not* work **very** well. Use HTML <em>tags</em>.</dd></dl>### 触碰显示提示框<pre class="line-numbers language-angular2html" data-language="angular2html"><code class="language-angular2html">&#123;% hint &#39;body_text&#39; &#39;hint_text_1st_line&#39; &#39;hint_text_2nd_line&#39; ... %&#125;&#123;% hint &#39;触碰显示&#39; &#39;第一行提示1&#39; &#39;第二行提示2&#39; %&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><span class="hint--info hint--rounded hint--top" data-hint="第一行提示1第二行提示2" ontouchstart>触碰显示提示</span>正常文字]]></content>
      
      
